---
import SocialLinks from "./SocialLinks.astro";
---

<section class="py-32 px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <div
    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 text-sm mb-8"
  >
    <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
      <span
        class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"
      ></span>
      <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"
      ></span>
    </span>
    Disponible para nuevos proyectos
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6">
    Desarrollador Web Full Stack
  </h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
    Creo experiencias web excepcionales con código limpio y diseño moderno.
    Especializado en arquitectura escalable y soluciones de alto rendimiento.
  </p>

  <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a
        href="mailto:alexis@example.com"
        class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(37,99,235,0.5)] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >Hablemos →</a
      >
      <a
        href="#proyectos"
        class="border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30 hover:bg-white/5 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >Ver Proyectos</a
      >
    </div>
    <SocialLinks />
  </div>
</section>
